name: rosy
readme:
![Rosy](http://ff0000.github.com/rosy/rosy.png?) ##### An inheritable AMD Framework. [![Build Status](https://secure.travis-ci.org/ff0000/rosy.png?branch=master)](http://travis-ci.org/ff0000/rosy) ### Support Rosy is [verified to work](https://github.com/ff0000/rosy/wiki/Unit-Tests) in the following browsers:
Desktop iOS Android
Chrome (latest) Chrome (latest) Chrome (Nexus 7)
Safari (latest) Safari (latest)
Firefox (latest)
Internet Explorer (7+)
### Documentation For documentation and implementation details, check out the [wiki.](https://github.com/ff0000/rosy/wiki)
